==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prolongation
<hw>Pro`lon*ga"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>prolongation</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of lengthening in space or in time;
extension; protraction.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which forms an additional length.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prolonge</ent>⟦br⟧
